snippet.title: Alien Escape - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
In Alien Escape you help Timmy escaping out of the castle by changing the gravity.
Save his friends and at the end of all defeat the evil boss!

A challenging puzzle platformer releasing on Nintendo Switch and PC on June 25th.

Other console versions and a mobile version will follow in a couple of months.

https://www.korion.de
